'''伊本·拉班'''全名'''库什亚·伊本·拉班'''（Kushyar ibn Labban 971年-1029年），是一名中世纪時期的[[伊朗人|伊朗裔]][[波斯|波斯]][[吉兰省|吉蘭]]人，数学家、天文学家和地理學家。<ref>{{cite book | last = Hockey | first = Thomas | title = Biographical encyclopedia of astronomers | publisher = Springer | location = New York | year = 2014 | page=1074 | isbn = 9781441999184 |quote=Kushyar ibn Labban was an eminent Iranian astronomer known for his work on astronomical handbooks (zijes) in addition to his work in mathematics and astrology.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Selin | first = Helaine | title = Encyclopaedia of the history of science, technology, and medicine in non-western cultures | url = https://archive.org/details/encyclopaediahis00seli_136 | publisher = Springer | location = Berlin New York | year = 2008 | isbn = 9781402049606 | page=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopaediahis00seli_136/page/241 241] | accessdate=2 December 2016 | quote=Another important early treatise that publicized decimal numbers was Iranian mathematician and astronomer Kūshyār ibn Labbān’s (fl. 1000) Kitāb fī usūl hisāb al-hind (Principles of Hindu Reckoning), a leading arithmetic textbook.}}</ref>主要著作包括《[[印度算术原理|印度算术原理]]》（Kitab fi usul hisab al-Hind）和天文学、地理学方面的书籍。伊本·拉班是著名波斯数学家[[阿嘛德·纳萨为|阿嘛德·纳萨为]]的老师。

